#ROOM
Vnum     19552
Name     &BThe Sunken Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The murky waters of the Pool of Tears give way to a large, air-filled 
stone chamber. The ceiling is high and supported by pillars 
carved in the image of massive, winged serpents. To the 
north, a grand staircase winds upward into the main body of 
the temple.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    36090
Desc      Return to the surface of the swamp.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    19553
Desc      The spiral staircase.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     19553
Name     &BThe Grand Spiral - Lower&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive stone ramp winds around a central vertical shaft. 
The air is stagnant and smells of old incense. Skeletal trolls 
in rusted armor stand in alcoves along the walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    19552
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    19554
Desc      The spiral continues.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 19500 10 19553
Reset O 0 19546 10 19553
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     19554
Name     &BThe Grand Spiral - Middle&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Halfway up the main shaft. The walls are covered in intricate 
bas-reliefs depicting the rise of the Blood God, Hakkar. 
A narrow doorway to the east leads toward the balcony levels.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    19553
Desc      Lower spiral.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    19555
Desc      Upper spiral.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    19561
Desc      The lower balconies.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 19512 10 19554
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
