Name     &BThe Grand Spiral - Upper&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You reach the top of the main staircase. The air here is 
thick with the scent of green dragon scales and magical 
exhaust. To the north, a set of heavy doors leads into 
the inner sanctum of the Shade.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    19554
Desc      Middle spiral.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
