#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    19576
Desc      Toward Jammal'an's Sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 19515 5 19555
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     19556
Name     &BThe Statue Room - The Pit&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive, circular chamber deep in the temple's basement. 
Six large stone statues surround a central altar. The 
water here is waist-deep and filled with primordial ooze.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    19553
Desc      Return to the staircase.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    19557
Desc      Toward the deep basement.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 19518 10 19556
#ENDROOM

