Name     &BThe Deep Basement - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A dark, damp tunnel leading away from the statue room. 
The sound of slithering scales echoes off the walls, and 
the air is humid and difficult to breathe.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
